CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 7, 1951, pg. 6 reads: "Owl Cab Company "Hello Girls" - Standing, left to right: Miss Helen Early, supervisor; Mrs. Betty Blackwell, Mrs. Lillie Mae Lott. Seated: Miss Alma Terry, Mrs. Dorothy Gaitor"
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Owl Cab telephone operators, from left, seated: Alma Terry and Dorothy Gaitor; standing: Helen Early, Betty Blackwell, and Lillie Mae Lott, posed behind table in interior with exposed brick wall in background, another version
